text: Hymenaeus may refer to: * Hymen (god), also known as Hymenaios, a deity in Greek mythology * Hymenaeus (biblical figure), a heretical teacher in Ephesus * Grady Louis McMurtry, also known as Hymenaeus Alpha * William Breeze (Hymenaeus Beta), his successor in the Caliphate Ordo Templi Orientis
title: Hymenaeus
